        question: "The nurse is administering fomepizole to a methanol-poisoned patient who is also undergoing hemodialysis. Which dosing adjustment is necessary?",
        options: ["Decrease the dose by 50% during hemodialysis","Hold fomepizole during hemodialysis sessions","Increase dosing frequency to every 4 hours during hemodialysis","Maintain the standard every 12-hour dosing schedule"],
        correct: 2,
